thread.title: BRIEF-Nevro Sees Q4 Revenue $97.4 Million To $97.9 Million

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Nevro Sees Q4 Revenue $97.4 Million To $97.9 Million
text:
Jan 8 (Reuters) - Nevro Corp:
* NEVRO ANNOUNCES PRELIMINARY UNAUDITED FOURTH QUARTER AND FISCAL YEAR 2017 REVENUE
* SEES FY 2018 REVENUE $400 MILLION TO $410 MILLION * SEES Q4 REVENUE $97.4 MILLION TO $97.9 MILLION * SEES FY 2017 REVENUE $326.1 MILLION TO $326.6 MILLION * FY2018 REVENUE VIEW $401.7 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* Q4 REVENUE VIEW $90.4 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S * FY2017 REVENUE VIEW $319.0 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
